🧠 Deeper Insight (Very Important)

Cursor pagination optimizes:

Performance

Consistency

Scalability

But sacrifices:

Random access

Offset pagination optimizes:

Random access

Simplicity

But sacrifices:

Performance at scale

It’s always a tradeoff.

Good engineers choose based on use case.

